summary: This is a simple Gold Coin replacer, replaces the vanilla gold coin with a new Dwemer Coin. The design of the coin was inspired by Morrowind.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://img14.imageshack.us/img14/3448/cointitle.png[/img][/center]

=================
Requirements:
=================

Skyrim 1.8.151.0

=================
Description:
=================

This is a simple Gold Coin replacer, replaces the vanilla gold coin with a new Dwemer Coin. The design of the coin was inspired by Morrowind.

Comes with a new Model and a new Texture.

=================
Installation
=================

1. Extract the contents of the ZIP folder into your Data folder

=================
Un-Installation:
=================

1. Delete the files/folders associated with the mod

=================
Known Issues/Incompatibilities:
=================

Does not work with previous stand alone releases.

=================
